data.text:
Q: Where is Silapathar Railway Station?

A: Silapathar railway station is a small railway station in Assam, located in Dhemaji district of the state. Silapathar station falls under Rangiya division of NFR/Northeast Frontier railways.

Q: What is the station code of Silapathar railway station?

A: The station code of Silapathar railway station is SPTR.
